{"tid":1608653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Condom仔收完安家費出嚟頂有幾難? 我要成個政權倒台呀","createTime":"2019-10-01T11:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T12:21:40.000Z","uid":52609,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b35d0a26dafb67cc8319e326dee67bcbcd94188e","tid":1608653,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n打倒殺人政權<br />\n還我香港自治<br />\n民主萬歲</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nfrom 老豆搵仔<br />\n你地都戇鳩<br />\n咪撚再亂傳開槍黑警嘅流料<br />\n啲料傳得咁快睇來班曱甴真係好驚，渣渣聲推個人出嚟承擔責任就算<br />\n你班曱甴想鬆人？發夢都冇咁早<br />\n我哋正式宣布，搵到開槍狗都唔會出<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">三萬警犬共榮辱<br />\n全部都係殺人犯<br />\n狗仔全部都係殺人犯之子</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好咁弱智<br />\n咁大張好牌都唔識用<br />\n千祈唔好民間自己搵開槍狗出嚟<br />\n要交人都一哥交人 <br />\n千祈唔好自己搵 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣做即係將好嚴重嘅外交問題政治問題<br />\ndowngrade做法律問題</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好畀曱甴得逞"},{"pid":"9f4ed8f24c68b040c1598444add0baa6962603f8","tid":1608653,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"咪強調一個黑警<br />\n無number鬼知係邊個，隨時收完安家費出嚟頂<br />\n<br />\n三萬個全部都係黑警，重組警隊<br />\n打倒殺人政權"},{"pid":"ea1508471b62dc717cc948e28d4d1278e6225da6","tid":1608653,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"打倒殺人政權"},{"pid":"914bd45ca288289223ef1eab861dc49e210fc8f7","tid":1608653,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:17:08.000Z","msg":"諗下被人私刑個阿伯<br />\n交左幾個condom仔之後<br />\n就無人追擊成個警隊"},{"pid":"f7c7c80c065550e2b250e9a4d0e89f933b488a06","tid":1608653,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a743a6f5ca378d859c899cfba4f9852b84d72ace","tid":1608653,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:20:58.0